<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>6706</hymn_number>
<author>ạ̹btsạm, nbyl</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (ʿmry mạ dqt sʿạdh ḥqyqyh fy bʿdy ʿnk yạrby wfạdyạ
 slạmk byfrḥny knt tạyh fy ạ̉whạm ạlʿạlm
 rfḍt ḥbk rfḍt slạmk wạlʿạlm lm ysẖbʿny)2
 jyt ly yạrby lmstly qlby ḥrrtny wfrḥtny
 ḥbk bysbyny sẖkẖṣk byʿzyny ạ̉nạ mdywn lḥbk yạ yswʿ
 (slạmk rby byṭmny dạymạaⁿ mhmạ ạ̹n kạn ḥwly tʿb fy ạlṭryq
 bạstryḥ ʿnd qdmyk rby mạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlʿsẖrh wyạk
 mn sạʿẗ lmạ ʿsẖt fy ḥmạk wạlfrḥ byfyḍ mny)2
 hlylwyạ mjdạaⁿ yạ yswʿ ạ̹jʿlny dạymạaⁿ dạymạaⁿ fy kẖḍwʿ
 (rby qwyny dạymạaⁿ kẖlyny ạ̉sẖhd wạ̉kẖbr bjmạlk)2</lyrics>
<title>ʿmry mạdqt sʿạdẗ ḥqyqyẗ</title>
</song>